						</div>
						<div>
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
									<path d="M3.2 14.222V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h13.6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10.222m-17.6 0h17.6m-17.6 0l-1.48 5.234A2 2 0 0 0 3.644 22h16.712a2 2 0 0 0 1.924-2.544l-1.48-5.234" />
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11 19h2m1-13l2 2l-2 2m-4-4L8 8l2 2" />
								</g>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					
				</div>
				<h3 id="index-others-h">Andere beschreiben mich so:</h3>
				<div id="index-others-container">
					<div>
						<p class="index-others-container-txt" >Hallo dieser Text ist ein kleiner Test. Ich will wissen, wie gut das klappt :D</p>
						<p class="index-others-container-name">@feuerstein</p>
						<img class="index-others-container-img" src="https://media.mastodon.de/accounts/avatars/110/961/284/696/885/054/original/30302bd5153ebb84.png">
